AI-generated%20recipes%20are%20popping%20up%20all%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-apps%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20circulating%20from%20pages%20that%20pump%20out%20eerie-looking%20images%20of%20food%20by%20the%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-facebook-ban-ai-slop-images-shrimp-jesus-why-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShrimp%20Jesus%26quot%3B%20type%20of%20AI-generated%20slop%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20this%20food-centered%20stuff%20flies%20under%20the%20radar%20because%20it%20looks%20so%20much%20like%20an%20existing%20genre%20that's%20already%20all%20over%20social%20media%3A%20gooey%20cheese-pull%20style%20food%20porn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20while%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Fcrochet%2Fcomments%2F12nis8u%2Fgrandmas_crochet_combat_tanks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimage%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20an%20old%20woman%20standing%20next%20to%20a%20crocheted%20tank%20is%20obviously%20fake%2C%20no%20one%20is%20going%20to%20bat%20an%20eye%20at%20a%20recipe%20for%20a%20healthy%20weeknight%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20looked%20into%20a%20few%20Facebook%20pages%20that%20are%20posting%20what%20appear%20to%20be%20AI-generated%20recipes%20with%20AI-generated%20images.%20(How'd%20I%20come%20to%20suspect%3F%20The%20images%20had%20telltale%20signs%20of%20AI%2C%20like%20disappearing%20tines%20on%20a%20fork%20or%20weirdly%20shaped%20fingers%20or%20distorted%20edges.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20found%20most%20surprising%3A%20People%20are%20actually%20%3Cem%3Ecooking%3C%2Fem%3E%20these%20AI-generated%20recipes.%20Sometimes%2C%20they're%20even%20enjoying%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20had%20to%20get%20in%20on%20the%20kitchen%20action%20myself.%20I%20made%20one%20of%20the%20salmon%20dishes%20%E2%80%94%20let's%20call%20it%20%26quot%3BSalmonGPT.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225c0e9d5d-2db9-480e-890e-b4002e9a7f05%5C%22%3EOne%20popular%20Facebook%20page%20pumps%20out%20recipes%20each%20hour%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221209%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lora%20Chef%20Facebook%20page%20with%20food%20thumbnails%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67af97f46630eb10385cb8ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22780%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20%26quot%3BLora%20Chef%26quot%3B%20Facebook%20page%20has%20photo%20after%20photo%20of%20recipes%20featuring%20the%20same%20sauce.%3Cp%3EScreengrab%2FLora%20Chef%20Facebook%20page%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20focused%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fprofile.php%3Fid%3D61562131926422%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELora%20Chef%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Facebook%20page%20with%20more%20than%20150%2C000%20followers.%20%3Cspan%3EIt's%20one%20of%20many%20similar%20recipe%20pages%20with%20some%20telltale%20AI%20features%20that%20are%20proliferating%20across%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20The%20page's%20profile%20picture%20features%20an%20attractive%20brunette%20woman.%20It%20also%20links%20out%20to%20a%20website%2C%20which%20offers%20a%20signup%20for%20an%20email%20recipe%20newsletter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20phone%20number%20on%20the%20Lora%20Chef%20Facebook%20page%20didn't%20work%20when%20I%20tried%20multiple%20times%20over%20several%20days.%20I%20emailed%20the%20contact%20address%20listed%20and%20initially%20got%20a%20reply%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Bhi%2C%20how%20can%20I%20help%20you%3F%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20account%20didn't%20respond%20to%20subsequent%20emails%20with%20my%20questions%2C%20like%20who%20was%20behind%20the%20page%20and%20to%20confirm%20it%20was%20using%20AI.%20I%20also%20sent%20a%20Facebook%20direct%20message%20and%20didn't%20get%20a%20reply.%20According%20to%20the%20page's%20%26quot%3Babout%26quot%3B%20section%2C%20its%20managers%20are%20located%20in%20Morocco%20and%20Turkey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20theory%2C%20AI-generated%20images%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20labeled%20on%20Meta%20platforms%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20tricky%20task%2C%20and%20let's%20be%20honest%3A%20AI%20chicken%20parm%20isn't%20going%20to%20destabilize%20democracy.%20Meta%20pointed%20to%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabout.fb.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F04%2Fmetas-approach-to-labeling-ai-generated-content-and-manipulated-media%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epolicy%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20declined%20to%20comment%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELora%20Chef%20has%20lately%20been%20posting%20a%20new%20recipe%20to%20Facebook%20about%20once%20an%20hour%2C%20which%20means%20there%20are%20hundreds%2C%20maybe%20thousands%2C%20of%20recipes.%20(I%20gave%20up%20scrolling%20when%20I%20got%20as%20far%20back%20as%20December%2C%20but%20the%20page%20was%20created%20in%20July%202024.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20images%20all%20have%20a%20similar%20appearance.%20Specifically%2C%20almost%20all%20the%20dishes%20have%20the%20same%20beige%20sauce%20oozing%20out%20over%20the%20food%20%E2%80%94%20usually%20from%20a%20spoon%2C%20fork%2C%20chopsticks%2C%20or%20some%20other%20utensil%20that%20only%20AI%20could%20dream%20up.%20The%20sauce%20looks%20oddly%20similar%20in%20all%20the%20dishes%2C%20but%20in%20their%20titles%2C%20the%20recipes%20refer%20to%20it%20as%20a%20garlic%20sauce%2C%20white%20sauce%2C%20cream%20sauce%2C%20garlic%20aioli%20dipping%20sauce%2C%20etc.%20(Even%20the%20desserts%20have%20the%20same-looking%20sauce.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dishes%20look%20reasonably%20appealing%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20them%20have%20comments%20from%20real%20people%20expressing%20things%20like%20%26quot%3Byummy!%26quot%3B%20or%20saying%20they'd%20like%20to%20try%20it.%20Very%20commonly%2C%20people%20tag%20a%20friend%20in%20the%20comments%20%E2%80%94%20perhaps%20suggesting%20it%20to%20a%20spouse%20for%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20food%20writer%20in%20Omaha%2C%20Nebraska%2C%20told%20me%20that%20AI%20recipes%20are%20latching%20onto%20something.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20see%20the%20interest%20people%20have%20in%20the%20recipes%2C%20which%20all%20feature%20trendy%20ingredients%20like%20cottage%20cheese%20%E2%80%94%20or%20heavily%20featuring%20protein%2C%20and%20all%20with%20very%20bright%2C%20appealing%20photos%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sarah%20Baker%20Hansen%2C%20who%20runs%20a%20food%20website%20and%20writes%20for%20the%20nonprofit%20Flatwater%20Free%20Press.%20%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20designed%20for%20clicks%2C%20shares%2C%20and%20comments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20she%20said%2C%20when%20looking%20at%20recipes%20across%20lots%20of%20different%20Facebook%20pages%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20pretty%20obvious%20which%20posts%20are%20computer-generated%20and%20which%20are%20actual%20recipes%20made%20by%20humans%2C%20with%20photographs%20taken%20by%20humans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225ce2f22c-48e1-49ac-941e-89edb588a8b3%5C%22%3EThese%20people%20actually%20cooked%20the%20recipes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20comments%20on%20the%20Lora%20Chef%20page%20for%20a%20vegetables%20and%20tzatziki%20dip%2C%20Lizzy%20Mimzy%20said%20the%20sauce%20ended%20up%20tasting%20exactly%20like%20ranch.%20When%20I%20chatted%20with%20her%2C%20she%20said%20she%20had%20made%20several%20other%20dishes%20from%20the%20page%20but%20hadn't%20realized%20it%20was%20AI.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20wondering%20why%20the%20pictures%20looked%20like%20all%20similar%20colors%20and%20textures%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI-generated%20kinda%20takes%20away%20from%20the%20real%20love%20people%20put%20in%20their%20food%2C%26quot%3B%20Mimzy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJacq%20Dolittle%20commented%20that%20her%20boyfriend%20had%20made%20the%20%26quot%3Bgrilled%20chicken%20and%20broccoli%20bowl%20with%20creamy%20garlic%20sauce%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20page's%20most%20popular%20posts%2C%20with%20more%20than%202%2C600%20comments%20and%2025%2C000%20shares%20on%20Facebook.%20She%20told%20me%20it%20turned%20out%20a%20little%20bland%20but%20still%20good.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20heard%20AI%20recipes%20are%20always%20a%20bit%20off%2C%20LOL%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20dishes%20seemed%20to%20have%20some%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20popular%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto%2F%3Ffbid%3D122129744558404397%26set%3Dpb.61562131926422.-2207520000%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParmesan-crusted%20chicken%20recipe%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20several%20comments%20mentioned%20that%20the%20chicken%20needed%20to%20be%20pan-fried%2C%20not%20baked%2C%20to%20achieve%20the%20kind%20of%20brown%20crust%20in%20the%20image.%20One%20comment%20read%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20realize%20this%20was%20AI-generated%20until%20after%20I%20made%20it%2C%20and%20I'm%20disappointed%20in%20myself.%20The%20sauce%20isn't%20too%20bad%20aside%20from%20being%20watery%2C%20and%20the%20chicken%20itself%20tastes%20like%20nothing%20LOL.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22213673a5-3d36-46dc-9440-8331cd3c6c98%5C%22%3EI%20made%20AI%20salmon%20with%20avocado%20crema%20and%20lime%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22AI-generated%20recipe%20salmon%20dish%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67afbaf2eb4be2fff9a4c632%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20raw%20ingredients%20for%20my%20AI-generated%20salmon%20dish.%3Cp%3EKatie%20Notopoulos%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20to%20test%20out%20one%20of%20these%20recipes%20for%20myself.%20I'm%20no%20stranger%20to%20trying%20AI-suggested%20food%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-glue-pizza-i-tried-it-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20once%20made%20pizza%20with%20glue%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20sauce%20because%20Google's%20AI%20answers%20suggested%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20Lora%20Chef%20page%2C%20I%20picked%20a%20recent%20recipe%20for%20salmon%20with%20a%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0you%20guessed%20it%20%E2%80%94%20white%20sauce%20because%20it%20seemed%20relatively%20easy%2C%20and%20I%20needed%20it%20easy%20because%20I%20am%20a%20very%2C%20very%20bad%20cook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cream%20sauce%20called%20for%20a%20food%20processor%2C%20which%20I%20wasn't%20entirely%20happy%20to%20have%20to%20drag%20out%20of%20the%20cupboard%2C%20but%20OK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20salmon%20called%20for%20some%20spices%20on%20top%20and%20then%20pan-frying%20in%20olive%20oil.%20My%20husband%2C%20the%20chef%20of%20the%20family%2C%20remarked%20that%20canola%20oil%20would%20typically%20be%20preferred%20because%20of%20its%20higher%20smoke%20point.%20(Perhaps%20this%20was%20an%20AI%20mistake.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20I%20served%20it%20over%20rice%2C%20and%20it%20was%20...%20%3Cem%3Efine%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Somewhat%20bland%2C%20both%20the%20fish%20and%20the%20sauce.%20But%20I%20ate%20the%20AI%20food%20and%20lived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22AI-generated%20salmon%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67afbb5aeb4be2fff9a4c650%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20final%20product%3A%20My%20AI-spawned%20salmon.%20Bon%20appetit!%3Cp%3EKatie%20Notopoulos%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAI%2C%20it%20seems%2C%20is%20capable%20of%20generating%20acceptable%20recipes%20for%20common%20dishes.%20This%20makes%20sense%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20a%20lot%20about%20cooking%20that%20is%20replicated%20over%20and%20over%2C%20and%20the%20same%20steps%20tend%20to%20follow%20each%20other%20in%20the%20process.%20This%20is%20perfect%20for%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20though%20generative%20AI%20can%20do%20some%20things%20capably%2C%20it%20doesn't%20always%20do%20things%20well.%20Real%20recipe%20writing%20is%20nuanced%20and%20difficult%20work%20%E2%80%94%20cooks%20test%20out%20each%20step%20and%20use%20their%20knowledge%20to%20avoid%20pitfalls.%20For%20example%2C%20my%20salmon%20called%20for%20sesame%20seeds%20on%20top%20(I%20skipped%20them)%2C%20but%20those%20seeds%20probably%20would've%20burned%20in%20the%20pan%20(although%20they%20would%20have%20been%20good%20for%20baked%20or%20roasted%20salmon).%20A%20human%20recipe%20writer%20would've%20intuitively%20known%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20scale%20of%20what%20harm%20AI-generated%20content%20flooding%20Facebook%20might%20do%2C%20recipes%20are%20certainly%20not%20like%20political%20misinformation%20or%20a%20financial%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20unlike%20other%20AI-generated%20stuff%2C%20which%20might%20just%20elicit%20a%20comment%20or%20a%20%26quot%3Blike%26quot%3B%20from%20an%20unsuspecting%20person%2C%20there%20are%20actually%20people%20out%20there%20spending%20their%20evenings%20cooking%20and%20eating%20these%20recipes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-recipes-ai-food-how-to-make-cook-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739620022000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67af9ba27bb3f854015cfbef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-recipes-ai-food-how-to-make-cook-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Recipes%20written%20by%20AI%20are%20all%20over%20Facebook.%20Some%20people%20are%20making%20them%20%E2%80%94%20with%20mixed%20results.%20I%20had%20to%20try%20it%20for%20myself%3A%20Behold%2C%20my%20AI%20salmon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22knotopoulos%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Notopoulos)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-recipes-ai-food-how-to-make-cook-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Errol%20Musk%20Slams%20Elon's%20Fatherhood%3A%20%26quot%3B