JP%20leader%20became%20the%20state's%20chief%20minister%20in%202001.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlamming%20Mr%20Reddy%2C%20the%20BJP%20said%20the%20Telangana%20chief%20minister%20wanted%20to%20hog%20headlines%20by%20making%20such%20comments%20because%20he%20does%20not%20do%20any%20work%20and%20had%20failed%20to%20fulfil%20the%20promises%20he%20had%20made%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Telangana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20Congress%20event%20on%20Friday%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20said%20in%20Telugu%2C%20%26quot%3BPM%20Modi%20claims%20to%20be%20from%20a%20backward%20class%2C%20but%20he%20is%20not%20from%20a%20backward%20class%20by%20birth.%20He%20is%20a%20legally%20converted%20backward%20class.%20I%20am%20choosing%20my%20words%20carefully.%20Till%20he%20became%20chief%20minister%20in%202001%2C%20he%20was%20among%20the%20forward%20castes.%20After%20he%20became%20chief%20minister%2C%20he%20shifted%20his%20caste's%20category%20from%20forward%20to%20backward%20by%20enacting%20a%20legislation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BHe%20says%20he%20is%20in%20the%20chair%20as%20a%20backward%20class.%20He%20may%20hold%20a%20caste%20certificate%20as%20a%20backward%20class%20but%20his%20mindset%20is%20anti-backward%20class%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Telangana%20chief%20minister%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20Spokesperson%20RP%20Singh%20said%20Mr%20Reddy%20was%20resorting%20to%20making%20such%20statements%20to%20remain%20relevant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Mr%20Reddy)%20does%20not%20do%20any%20work%20and%20wants%20to%20ensure%20he%20makes%20headlines%20by%20making%20such%20controversial%20statements.%20He%20had%20earlier%20said%20(former%20chief%20minister)%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%20had%20'Bihari%20genes'%2C%20thereby%20insulting%20all%20of%20Bihar.%20He%20should%20talk%20only%20after%20finding%20out%20all%20the%20facts%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EK%20Laxman%2C%20the%20BJP's%20OBC%20(Other%20Backward%20Classes)%20Morcha%20national%20president%2C%20said%20Congress%20MP%20and%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20had%20made%20a%20similar%20statement%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr%20Reddy's%20comment%20on%20PM%20Modi's%20caste%20is%20absolutely%20false.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20had%20also%20made%20a%20similar%20remark%20and%20fallen%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20people.%20Why%20do%20people%20from%20the%20Congress%20keep%20commenting%20on%20the%20PM's%20caste%3F%20Revanth%20Reddy%20made%20the%20comment%20to%20keep%20his%20leaders%20happy.%20Mr%20Reddy%20could%20not%20fulfil%20the%20promises%20and%20guarantees%20that%20he%20made%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Telangana%2C%20who%20are%20angry%2C%20%C2%A0and%20is%20making%20such%20statements%20to%20distract%20from%20the%20real%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPanel's%20Clarification%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20had%20made%20a%20similar%20statement%20last%20year%2C%20the%20National%20Commission%20of%20Backward%20classes%20had%20said%20that%20the%20notification%20for%20inclusion%20of%20the%20Modh%20Ghanchi%20caste%20in%20the%20State%20List%20of%20OBC%20was%20issued%20by%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20on%20July%2025%2C%201994.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNational%20Commission%20for%20Backward%20Classes%20tendered%20advice%20to%20Union%20Government%20on%2015.11.1997%20for%20inclusion%20of%20Modh-Ghanchi%20in%20the%20Central%20List%20of%20OBCs%20for%20the%20State%20of%20Gujarat%20and%20Gazette%20Notification%20for%20the%20same%20was%20issued%20on%2027.10.1999...%20It%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20when%20both%20of%20above%20decisions%20for%20inclusion%20of%20Modh-Ghanchi%20in%20the%20State%20List%20of%20OBCs%20as%20well%20as%20in%20the%20Central%20List%20of%20OBCs%20were%20taken%2C%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%20held%20no%20legislative%20or%20executive%20position%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20commission%20had%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaste%20Survey%20Row%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Telangana%20government%20tabled%20some%20details%20from%20a%20caste%20survey%20in%20the%20Assembly%20on%20February%204%2C%20opposition%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20BJP%20and%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao's%20BRS%20claimed%20that%20it%20was%20not%20comprehensive.%20Some%20leaders%20from%20within%20the%20Congress%20also%20said%20that%20there%20were%20some%20issues%20with%20the%20numbers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Telangana%20government%20then%20announced%20that%20a%20second%20round%20of%20the%20survey%20will%20be%20conducted%20to%20cover%203.1%25%20of%20the%20state's%20population%2C%20which%20did%20not%20participate%20in%20the%20first%20round%2C%20from%20Sunday%20to%20February%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739619360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F40vcdoac_narendra-modi-revanth-reddy_625x300_04_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-telangana-chief-minister-backward-class-revanth-reddy-claims-pm-not-from-backward-class-by-birth-bjp-slams-him-7717201%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20a%20row%20over%20the%20caste%20survey%20in%20Telangana%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Revanth%20Reddy%20has%20said%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20not%20from%20a%20backward%20class%20by%20birth%20but%20belongs%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Blegally%20converted%20backward%20class%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98A%20Letter%20to%20David%E2%80%99%20Director%20Tom%20Shoval%20and%20Producer%20Nancy%20Spielberg%20on%20Transcending%20%E2%80%98Carnage%E2%80%99%20in%20Their%20Homage%20to%20Hamas%20Hostage%20David%20Cunio%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739619303000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FA-Letter-to