%20apps.%20Over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20weeks%2C%20I've%20relied%20on%20it%20to%20quickly%20understand%20whether%20a%20pile%20of%20emails%2C%20texts%2C%20or%20Slack%20notifications%20needs%20my%20immediate%20attention.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20times%20when%20a%20notification%20summary%20is%20too%20short%20or%20generic%20to%20be%20useful.%20It%20can%20sometimes%20miss%20the%20context.%20For%20example%2C%20it%20incorrectly%20summarized%20a%20handful%20of%20newspaper%20headlines%20and%20wrote%20%26quot%3BNetanyahu%20arrested%26quot%3B%20for%20a%20report%20about%20the%20International%20Criminal%20Court%20issuing%20an%20arrest%20warrant%20for%20the%20Israeli%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20then%2C%20Apple%20has%20paused%20notification%20summaries%20for%20news%20and%20entertainment%20apps.%20You%20can%20also%20manually%20pick%20which%20apps'%20alerts%20are%20summarized%20or%20switch%20off%20the%20function%20altogether.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222a0acde4-bf9a-4f81-905d-16c30ec5df5e%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20new%20setting%20mutes%20non-urgent%20notifications%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20Apple%20Intelligence%20tool%20that%20has%20reduced%20my%20screentime%20is%20the%20%26quot%3BReduce%20Interruptions%20Focus%26quot%3B%20setting.%20Apple's%20new%20software%2C%20the%20inner%20workings%20of%20which%20we%20don't%20know%20much%20about%2C%20analyzes%20each%20alert's%20urgency%20based%20on%20its%20content%20and%20only%20shows%20the%20ones%20its%20AI%20models%20think%20would%20matter%20to%20you%20while%20hiding%20the%20rest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20I%20place%20my%20iPhone%20in%20this%20mode%2C%20it%20typically%20hides%20non-essential%20correspondence%2C%20like%20sales%20alerts%2C%20forwards%20on%20messaging%20apps%2C%20or%20reservation%20confirmations%2C%20and%20notifies%20me%20for%20others%20with%20labels%20like%20%26quot%3BMaybe%20Important.%26quot%3B%20For%20example%2C%20it%20didn't%20ping%20me%20about%20a%20news%20link%20someone%20texted%20me%20but%20did%20alert%20me%20bout%20another%20message%20confirming%20dinner%20plans%20from%20the%20same%20person.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221a9d5d0f-70b6-45be-9d3c-76b8e58fc792%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESiri%20is%20more%20accurate%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20Apple%20Intelligence%20updates%2C%20Siri%20now%20converses%20naturally%20and%20is%20more%20contextually%20aware.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you%20ask%20a%20follow-up%20question%20to%20the%20initial%20%26quot%3BHey%20Siri%2C%26quot%3B%20now%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20repeat%20details%20from%20the%20intial%20request.%20If%20you%20stutter%20mid-conversation%20or%20converse%20as%20you%20would%20normally%2C%20it%20won't%20lose%20track%20of%20your%20question.%20A%20request%20like%20%26quot%3BSiri%2C%20set%20a%20timer%20for%2010%20minutes%2C%20wait%2C%20sorry%2C%20make%20that%2015%26quot%3B%20results%20in%20a%2015-minute%20timer%20being%20set%20%E2%80%94%20not%20the%20classic%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20quite%20understand%26quot%3B%20reply.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20Apple%20Intelligence%2C%20Siri%20is%20also%20far%20more%20accurate%20at%20performing%20actions%20inside%20other%20apps%2C%20like%20texting%20someone%20on%20WhatsApp.%20Siri%20has%20always%20been%20notorious%20for%20falling%20short%20in%20voice%20detection%2C%20and%20this%20update%20irons%20out%20these%20basic%20issues.%20In%20future%20updates%2C%20Apple%20has%20said%20Siri%20will%20let%20you%20execute%20more%20complex%20workflows%20hands-free%20on%20third-party%20services%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20a%20smart%20assistant%20that%20can%20control%20your%20entire%20phone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f9e0bd94-bc4c-4121-9a3f-79e5f2c54e49%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESiri%20%2B%20ChatGPT%20%3D%20happy%20Apple%20user%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Siri%20upgrade%20that%20I%20use%20the%20most%20is%20its%20ability%20to%20consult%20ChatGPT.%20When%20Siri%20doesn't%20have%20an%20answer%2C%20it%20forwards%20it%20to%20OpenAI's%20chatbot%2C%20which%2C%20in%20most%20cases%2C%20does.%20The%20ChatGPT%20addition%20is%20especially%20effective%20for%20analyzing%20a%20visual%20on%20your%20phone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20can%20ask%20Siri%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20on%20my%20screen%3F%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20will%20prompt%20ChatGPT%20to%20describe%20it.%20Pressing%20and%20holding%20the%20new%20Camera%20Control%20button%20opens%20up%20a%20Visual%20Intelligence%20interface%2C%20where%20I%20can%20take%20a%20picture%2C%20and%20ask%20questions%20about%20it%20to%20ChatGPT%20or%20look%20up%20its%20contents%20on%20Google.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20last%20week%2C%20I've%20taken%20pictures%20of%20books%20I've%20completed%20and%20used%20Visual%20Intelligence%20to%20find%20new%2C%20similar%20ones%20or%20to%20prepare%20a%20dinner%20menu%20to%20pair%20with%20a%20bottle%20of%20wine%20I%20was%20gifted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilar%20functions%20have%20been%20available%20on%20third-party%20apps%2C%20but%20having%20them%20built%20into%20iOS%20makes%20them%20much%20more%20convenient.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20Apple's%20solutions%20keep%20your%20sensitive%20data%20private.%20You%20can%20not%20only%20use%20the%20ChatGPT%20integration%20without%20an%20account%2C%20but%20Apple%20also%20explicitly%20prevents%20OpenAI%20from%20training%20its%20models%20on%20your%20conversations%20and%20media.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20not%20perfect%20yet.%20Often%2C%20it%20takes%20longer%20for%20me%20to%20get%20responses%20from%20Siri%20than%20to%20launch%20the%20ChatGPT%20app%20directly.%20Plus%2C%20there's%20no%20live%20mode%20like%20what%20others%20(Google%20Gemini%2C%20Perplexity)%20offer