0is%20impacting%20their%20business%20%E2%80%94%20and%20particularly%20their%20bacon%2C%20egg%2C%20and%20cheese%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20City's%20quintessential%20breakfast%20sandwich%20%E2%80%94%20enjoyed%20on%20the%20morning%20rush%20to%20work%20or%20a%203%20a.m.%20stumble%20home%20%E2%80%94%20typically%20costs%20between%20%244.50%20and%20%246.50%20depending%20on%20the%20neighborhood%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgothamist.com%2Fnews%2Finflation-egg-and-cheese-bird-flu-hits-nycs-staple-bodega-sandwich%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGothamist%3C%2Fa%3E%20previously%20reported.%20Yet%20many%20deli%20and%20bodega%20owners%20told%20BI%20that%20they've%20already%20raised%20or%20are%20considering%20raising%20the%20price%20of%20the%20staple%20by%20between%2050%20cents%20and%20%241.%20Their%20prices%20ranged%20from%20%245%20in%20Downtown%20Brooklyn%20to%20%248%20in%20the%20Financial%20District%20of%20Manhattan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sign%20at%20Best%20of%20NY%20Deli%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67afae80eb4be2fff9a4c2bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBest%20of%20NY%20Deli%20in%20Manhattan's%20Financial%20District%20posted%20a%20sign%20informing%20customers%20of%20the%20price%20hike.%3Cp%3EAlice%20Tecotzky%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20employees%20BI%20spoke%20to%20said%20they%20buy%20eggs%20in%2030-dozen-cases%2C%20which%20they%20said%20now%20cost%20more%20than%20%24200%20compared%20to%20around%20%2460%20before%20the%20Covid%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20price%20today%20is%20more%20than%20yesterday%2C%20the%20price%20yesterday%20is%20more%20than%20last%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20Jimmy%2C%20the%20manager%20at%20All%20American%20Deli%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20said.%20He%2C%20along%20with%20many%20of%20the%20other%20employees%20BI%20spoke%20to%2C%20asked%20to%20be%20identified%20by%20only%20his%20first%20name.%20Mohammad%2C%20a%20cashier%20at%20Slope%20Natural%20Plus%20in%20Brooklyn%20for%20the%20past%2017%20years%2C%20said%20everyone%20in%20the%20neighborhood%20is%20struggling%20because%20of%20the%20rising%20wholesale%20egg%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody%20is%20screaming%2C%20everybody%20is%20yelling%2C%20'Why%20is%20it%20so%20much%3F'%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20US%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-january-cpi-consumer-price-index-federal-reserve-interest-rates-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einflation%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20hotter%20than%20expected%20and%20the%20spike%20in%20food%20prices%20was%20largely%20driven%20by%20eggs.%20In%20January%2C%20egg%20prices%20shot%20up%2015.2%25%20compared%20to%20the%20month%20before%20and%2053%25%20year%20over%20year.%20Rhett%20Buttle%2C%20the%20co-executive%20director%20of%20the%20Small%20Business%20Roundtable%2C%20said%20that%20small%20businesses%20are%20particularly%20vulnerable%20to%20price%20volatility%20because%20they%20operate%20on%20tight%20margins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20egg%20price%20situation%20is%20a%20unique%20pressure%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI%20in%20an%20email.%20%26quot%3BDuring%20broader%20inflation%2C%20costs%20generally%20rose%20more%20gradually%20across%20the%20board%2C%20allowing%20some%20ability%20to%20adjust.%20This%20sudden%20spike%20in%20an%20essential%20ingredient%20creates%20immediate%20strain%20on%20working%20capital%20and%20makes%20it%20difficult%20for%20small%20businesses%20to%20maintain%20stable%20pricing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Eggs%20and%20bacon%20on%20a%20grill%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67afaeae7bb3f854015d009d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECustomers%20continue%20to%20order%20the%20staple%20breakfast%20sandwich%2C%20even%20amid%20the%20rising%20prices.%3Cp%3EAlice%20Tecotzky%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJimmy%20said%20that%20his%20profit-per-sandwich%20is%20lower%20and%20that%20he's%20also%20struggling%20with%20the%20price%20of%20bacon%2C%20which%20saw%20a%204%25%20year-over-year%20increase%2C%20according%20to%20the%20latest%20CPI%20report.%20Both%20Angel%20and%20Bernardo%20Martinez%2C%20the%20respective%20morning%20manager%20at%20Pace%20Gourmet%20Deli%20and%20an%20employee%20at%20Apple%20Gourmet%20Deli%20in%20the%20Financial%20District%2C%20said%20their%20profit%20margins%20are%20lower%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221629%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Menu%20at%20Apple%20Gourmet%20Deli%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67afaf2f6630eb10385cbeb5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222172%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20employee%20at%20Apple%20Gourmet%20Deli%20said%20they%20haven't%20raised%20prices%20yet%2C%20but%20will%20likely%20have%20to%20next%20week.%3Cp%3EAlice%20Tecotzky%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20employees%20BI%20talked%20to%20said%20that%20customers%20are%20still%20ordering%20egg%20sandwiches%20%E2%80%94%20as%20Mohammad%20put%20it%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey%20have%20to%20eat%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20and%20are%20generally%20understanding%20of%20the%20price%20hikes%2C%20which%20have%20also%20hit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrocery-stores-costco-trader-joes-limit-egg-purchases-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrocery%20stores%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Occasionally%2C%20though%2C%20people%20will%20grumble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHere%20and%20there%20people%20will%20complain%20about%20it%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20sure%20they're%20caught%20up%20on%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20Angel%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20not%20the%20one%20seeing%20the%20bill%20that%20we%20have