C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Ukraine%20would%20need%20security%20guarantees%20against%20the%20threat%20of%20another%20attack%20to%20give%20investors%20the%20confidence%20to%20take%20risks%20and%20make%20long-term%20commitments%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20Kuleba%2C%20the%20Ukrainian%20minister%2C%20said%20his%20ideas%20for%20Ukraine's%20economy%20are%20still%20uncharted%20territory%2C%20but%20that%20%26quot%3Bif%20we%20want%20to%20build%20a%20future%2C%20we%20have%20to%20start%26quot%3B%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BUkraine%20is%20open%20to%20virtually%20any%20idea%20that%20can%20boost%20economic%20growth%20and%20build%20a%20sustainable%20economy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdefense-tech-industry-key-ukraine-postwar-economy-former-foreign-minister-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739615461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ac9d3feb4be2fff9a45d98%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdefense-tech-industry-key-ukraine-postwar-economy-former-foreign-minister-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dmytro%20Kuleba%2C%20Ukraine's%20ex%20foreign%20minister%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20country%20could%20leverage%20military%20tech%20to%20grow%20its%20economy%20after%20the%20war.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tspirlet%40insider.com%20(Thibault%20Spirlet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdefense-tech-industry-key-ukraine-postwar-economy-former-foreign-minister-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Koln%2075%E2%80%99%20Director%20Ido%20Fluk%20on%2018-Year-Old%20Vera%20Brandes%20Who%20Organized%20Keith%20Jarrett%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98The%20Koln%20Concert%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20Clip%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2