f%20former%20CJI%20DY%20Chandrachud.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Is%20Abhinav%20Chandrachud%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhinav%20Chandrachud's%20family%20name%20carries%20weight%20in%20India's%20judicial%20circles.%20His%20father%20was%20appointed%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20in%20May%202016%20before%20becoming%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India.%20Despite%20his%20father's%20towering%20position%20in%20the%20judiciary%2C%20Abhinav%20had%20never%20before%20presented%20a%20case%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20during%20his%20father's%20tenure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20his%20farewell%20speech%20last%20year%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20(retd)%20Chandrachud%20shared%20an%20anecdote%20about%20his%20two%20sons%2C%20Abhinav%20and%20Chintan.%20He%20recalled%20how%20he%20had%20once%20asked%20them%20to%20appear%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20hoping%20to%20see%20them%20more%20often.%20Both%2C%20however%2C%20declined%20the%20offer%2C%20citing%20professional%20integrity%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20past%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20(retd)%20Chandrachud%20had%20also%20reflected%20on%20his%20own%20career.%20Between%201982%20and%201985%2C%20he%20refrained%20from%20appearing%20in%20any%20Indian%20court%20while%20pursuing%20his%20studies%20at%20Harvard.%20His%20father%2C%20Justice%20YV%20Chandrachud%2C%20was%20India's%20longest-serving%20Chief%20Justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhinav%20Chandrachud%20is%20also%20an%20accomplished%20academic%20and%20author.%20He%20holds%20a%20Doctor%20of%20the%20Science%20of%20Law%20(JSD)%20and%20a%20Master%20of%20the%20Science%20of%20Law%20(JSM)%20from%20Stanford%20Law%20School%2C%20where%20he%20was%20a%20Franklin%20Family%20Scholar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20his%20LinkedIn%20profile%2C%20he%20graduated%20from%20Government%20Law%20College%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20in%202008.%20He%20later%20pursued%20his%20Master%20of%20Laws%20(LLM)%20at%20Harvard%20Law%20School%20as%20a%20Dana%20Scholar.%20He%20has%20also%20worked%20as%20an%20associate%20attorney%20at%20Gibson%2C%20Dunn%20%26amp%3B%20Crutcher%2C%20an%20international%20law%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20his%20legal%20practice%2C%20he%20has%20authored%20several%20books%2C%20including%20Republic%20of%20Rhetoric%3A%20Free%20Speech%20and%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20(2017)%20and%20Supreme%20Whispers%3A%20Conversations%20with%20Judges%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%201980-1989%20(2018).%20His%20opinion%20pieces%20have%20been%20published%20in%20leading%20Indian%20newspapers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia%20Case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%20Police%20have%20summoned%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia%20to%20appear%20for%20questioning%20on%20Saturday%20over%20controversial%20remarks%20he%20made%20during%20a%20YouTube%20show.%20The%20police%20had%20initially%20asked%20him%20to%20appear%20on%20Thursday%2C%20but%20when%20he%20failed%20to%20do%20so%2C%20they%20issued%20a%20second%20summons%20for%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20police%20teams%20from%20both%20Mumbai%20and%20Assam%20arrived%20at%20Mr%20Allahbadia's%20residence%20in%20Versova%2C%20only%20to%20find%20it%20locked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20stems%20from%20remarks%20made%20by%20Mr%20Allahbadia%20on%20comedian%20Samay%20Raina's%20now-deleted%20YouTube%20show%2C%20'India's%20Got%20Latent'.%20His%20comments%2C%20perceived%20as%20crude%20and%20offensive%2C%20triggered%20widespread%20outrage%20and%20multiple%20complaints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Assam%20Police%20team%20investigating%20the%20matter%20met%20with%20officials%20from%20Maharashtra's%20Cyber%20Department%20on%20Thursday.%20They%20are%20particularly%20interested%20in%20questioning%20not%20only%20Allahbadia%20but%20also%20fellow%20YouTubers%20Ashish%20Chanchlani%2C%20Jaspreet%20Singh%2C%20and%20Apoorva%20Makhija%2C%20who%20were%20featured%20in%20the%20controversial%20episode.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20yet%20to%20set%20a%20fixed%20date%20for%20hearing%20the%20petition%20in%20which%20Abhinav%20Chandrachud%20appeared%20virtually%20before%20Chief%20Justice%20Khanna.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739615100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F4uljdhco_abhinav-chandrachud_625x300_15_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fabhinav-chandrachud-beerbiceps-samay-raina-dy-chandrachud-abhinav-chandrachud-lawyer-representing-ranveer-allahbadia-in-top-court-7716177%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20yet%20to%20set%20a%20fixed%20date%20for%20hearing%20the%20petition%20in%20which%20Abhinav%20Chandrachud%20appeared%20virtually%20before%20Chief%20Justice%20Khanna.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20startup%20boosting%20OpenAI's%20security%20is%20creating%20a%20new%20Silicon%20Valley%20in%20Nepal.%20Call%20it%20'Silicon%20Peaks.'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227509%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nepali%20workers%20at%20SecurityPal%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67aec330eb4be2fff9a4a5a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224901%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESecurityPal's%20base%20in%20Kathmandu%20employs%20close%20to%20200%20workers.%3Cp%3ESecurityPal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESecurityPal%20helps%20major%20AI%20companies%20complete%20security%20questionnaires.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20has%20been%20operating%20a%2024%2F7%20command%20center%20in%20Kathmandu%2C%20Nepal%20since%202023.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20technology%20talent%20just%20nestled%20amongst%20the%20foothills%2C%26quot%3B%20CEO%20Pukar%20Hamal%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAt%2010%3A00%20p.m.%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20it's%2011%3A