nsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fopenai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsequoia-leads-funding-round-generative-artificial-intelligence-startup-langchain-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELangchain%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-startup-anysphere-raises-a-new-funding-round-from-a16z-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECursor%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Its%20main%20focus%20is%20making%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20security%20review%20process%20easier%20for%20enterprise%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20these%20companies%20take%20on%20a%20new%20customer%20they%20are%20typically%20vetted%20by%20that%20customer%20through%20a%20security%20questionnaire.%20This%20complex%20document%20covers%20everything%20from%20how%20the%20company%20handles%20data%20to%20how%20it%20identifies%20vulnerabilities%20in%20its%20systems%20to%20the%20physical%20measures%20it%20takes%20to%20protect%20its%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20early%20days%2C%20SecurityPal's%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eemployees%20manually%20filled%20out%20every%20questionnaire.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20learned%20quickly%20was%20that%20there%20were%20ways%20to%20automate%20the%20steps%2C%26quot%3B%20Hamal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20when%20a%20company%20signs%20up%2C%20SecurityPal's%20analysts%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efirst%20spend%20time%20understanding%20the%20company's%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-promising-risk-and-compliance-fintechs-according-to-top-vcs-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecurity%20and%20compliance%3C%2Fa%3E%20posture.%20They'll%20parse%2C%20annotate%2C%20and%20add%20context%20to%20historical%20questionnaires%2C%20infrastructure%20documents%2C%20compliance%20reports%2C%20and%20other%20relevant%20information%20to%20create%20%26quot%3Bdiscrete%26quot%3B%20question%20and%20answer%20pairs%2C%20Hamal%20said.%20Using%20AI%2C%20the%20company%20has%20built%20a%20repository%20of%20over%202%20million%20pairs%2C%20which%20can%20be%20used%20for%20various%20customer%20requests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20rapid%20advancements%20in%20AI%20drive%20companies%20to%20adopt%20new%20tools%2C%20Hamal%20said%20he'd%20noticed%20more%20%26quot%3Bparanoia%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20questionnaires%20SecurityPal's%20clients%20receive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20companies%20just%20have%20a%20really%20hard%20time%20digesting%20what's%20actually%20happening%20with%20their%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20questions%20are%20different.%20They're%20more%20nuanced.%26quot%3B%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20large%20language%20model%20providers%2C%20for%20example%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey%20want%20to%20know%20how%20the%20model%20is%20used%2C%20how%20the%20model's%20trained%2C%20where%20it%20is%20hosted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecurityPal%20serves%20200%20to%20300%20customers%20annually.%20Most%20employ%20500%20to%201000%20people%20or%20more%2C%20and%20one-fifth%20of%20its%20customer%20base%20is%20publicly%20traded%20companies.%20At%20its%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecuritypal-raise-venture-capital-funding-without-pitch-deck-a16z-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESeries%20A%20funding%20round%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%202022%2C%20it%20was%20valued%20at%20%24105%20million.%20Hamal%20did%20not%20disclose%20the%20company's%20current%20valuation%20but%20said%20it's%20north%20of%20that%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227cb1cf32-0903-44fe-954a-5d2930899707%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20Silicon%20Valley%20to%20Silicon%20Peaks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227285%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pukar%20Hamal%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67aff5b37bb3f854015d0830%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESecurityPal's%2033-year-old%20CEO%2C%20Pukar%20Hamal%2C%20was%20born%20in%20Nepal.%3Cp%3ESecurityPal%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHamal%2C%20now%2033%2C%20left%20Kathmandu%20for%20New%20York%20when%20he%20was%207.%20He%20studied%20international%20relations%20at%20Stanford%20and%20planned%20to%20become%20a%20diplomat.%20He%20ultimately%20ended%20up%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%2C%20launching%20his%20first%20startup%2C%20Teamable%2C%20in%202016.%20It%20was%20acquired%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20SecurityPal%2C%20Hamal%20didn't%20initially%20have%20plans%20to%20launch%20a%20second%20base%20in%20his%20motherland.%20He%20was%20looking%20at%20places%20that%20were%20hours%20ahead%20of%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20like%20India%20and%20the%20Philippines%20%E2%80%94%20so%20when%20it%20was%20nighttime%20for%20his%20clients%2C%20his%20team%20could%20be%20hard%20at%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20was%20always%20skeptical%20about%20the%20talent%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Once%20he%20realized%20how%20many%20students%20Nepal%20was%20sending%20to%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20and%20Australia%2C%20though%2C%20he%20began%20to%20reconsider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%202000%20to%202016%2C%20the%20number%20of%20Nepali%20students%20enrolled%20in%20degree%20programs%20abroad%20surged%20by%20835%25%2C%20reaching%2044%2C255%20students%20by%202017%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwenr.wes.org%2F2018%2F04%2Feducation-in-nepal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20World%20Education%20News%20and%20Reviews.%20Nepal's%20ratio%20of%20international%20students%20to%20domestic%20students%20is%20also%20significantly%20higher%20than%20neighboring%20countries%20like%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20COVID-19%20hit%2C%20though%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emany%20students%20who%20went%20abroad%20returned%20to%20be%20closer%20to%20family%20and%20stayed.%20They%20were%20not%20only%20fluent%20in%20English%2C%20but%20also%20equipped%20with%20technical%20skills%20that%20rivaled%20those%20of%20workers%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20Hamal%20said.%20He%20saw%20potential%20in%20this%20pool%20of%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20trying%20to%20champion%20the%20term%20'Silicon%20Peaks'%20because%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20technology%20talent%20just%20nestled%20amongst%20the%20foothills%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEconomic%20growth%20in%20Nepal%20has%20steadily%20increased%20since%202018%2C%20when%20a%20new%20government%20was%20formed%20after%20years%20of%20political%20turmoil%20and%20peace%20negotiations.%20Between%202023%20and%202024%2C%20the%20services%20sector%20%E2%80%94%20including%20industries%20like%20tourism%2C%20real%20estate%2C%20and%20trade%20%E2%80%94%20was%20the%20greatest%20driver%20of%20Nepal's%20gross%20domestic%20product%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldbank.org%2Fen%2Fcountry%2Fnepal%2Foverview%23%3A~%3Atext%3DRECENT%2520ECONOMIC%2520DEVELOPMENTS%2C%252C%2520accommodation%252C%2520and%2520food%2520services.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20World%20Bank.%20Agriculture%20also%20plays%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20base%20in%20Kathmandu%2C%20Hamal%20is%20hoping%20to%20reshape%20how%20the%20world%20views%20Nepal's%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNepal's%20always%20been%20sort%20of%20like%20this%20feeder%20country%20of%20high-quality%20physical%20labor%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20He%20mentioned%20the%20Gurkhas%2C%20Nepali%20soldiers%20that%20the%20British%20East%20India%20Company%20began%20recruiting%20in%20the%20early%20nineteenth%20century%20as%20an%20elite%20fighting%20force%20or%20the%20scores%20of%20Nepali%20migrant%20workers%20who%20built%20stadiums%20in%20Qatar%20for%20the%202022%20FIFA%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20talent%20has%20always%20been%20there%2C%20but%20the%20perception%20was%20that%20it%20skewed%20more%20on%20the%20brawn%20side%2C%26quot%3B