eration%20fighter%20jet%20was%20developed%20for%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%20but%20is%20now%20in%20service%20with%20more%20than%20two%20dozen%20militaries%20around%20the%20world%2C%20including%20%E2%80%94%20as%20of%20last%20year%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Ukrainian%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20F-16%20was%20revolutionary%20from%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fold-popular-f-16-fighter-jet-still-packs-a-punch-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaircraft%20design%20philosophy%3C%2Fa%3E%20perspective%2C%20emerging%20as%20the%20first%20fly-by-wire%20fighter%20for%20improved%20air-to-air%20combat%20capabilities.%20But%20in%20the%20age%20of%20stealth%20aircraft%20and%20higher-end%20surface-to-air%20threats%2C%20the%20F-16%2C%20even%20with%20the%20upgrades%20the%20fighter%20has%20gotten%20over%20the%20years%20to%20ensure%20it%20still%20packs%20a%20punch%2C%20is%20losing%20its%20once%20formidable%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223624%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20US%20Air%20Force%20F-16%20fighter%20jet%20takes%20off%20from%20an%20airbase%20in%20Germany.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67af61f66630eb10385caa4e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20US%20Air%20Force%20F-16%20fighter%20jet%20takes%20off%20from%20an%20airbase%20in%20Germany.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20Boris%20Roessler%2Fpicture%20alliance%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20much-newer%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-strikes-iran-shows-f-35-ready-higher-level-war-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EF-35%20Lightning%20II%3C%2Fa%3E%20Joint%20Strike%20Fighter%20is%20a%20supersonic%20stealth%20aircraft%20that%20took%20its%20first%20flight%20nearly%2020%20years%20ago.%20The%20platform%20has%20evolved%20tremendously%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20aircra