ned%20on%20Saturday%2C%20following%20successful%20mediation%20efforts%20by%20Egyptian%20and%20Qatari%20officials.%20The%20hostages%2C%20who%20were%20seized%20by%20Hamas%20militants%20during%20an%20attack%20on%20October%207%2C%202023%2C%20were%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20International%20Committee%20of%20the%20Red%20Cross%2C%20which%C2%A0then%20transported%20them%20to%20Israeli%20forces.%20The%20military%20has%20confirmed%20that%20the%20freed%20hostages%20are%20now%20back%20in%20Israel.%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20is%20part%20of%20a%20prisoner%20swap%20agreement%20that%20will%20see%20369%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20and%20detainees%20freed%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20three%20Israeli%20hostages.%20The%20agreement%20is%20a%20significant%20development%20in%20the%20ongoing%20efforts%20to%20maintain%20a%20fragile%20ceasefire%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20hostages%2C%20who%20were%20held%20captive%20for%20several%20months%2C%20were%20seen%20being%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20Red%20Cross%20in%20Gaza's%20southern%20city%20of%20Khan%20Yunis.%20They%20were%20reportedly%20in%20good%20health%20and%20were%20seen%20clutching%20gift%20bags%20and%20certificates%20marking%20the%20end%20of%20their%20captivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20situation%20remains%20volatile%2C%20with%20tensions%20running%20high%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas.%20The%20Israeli%20military%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20blocking%20aid%20from%20entering%20Gaza%2C%20which%20has%20exacerbated%20the%20humanitarian%20crisis%20in%20the%20region.%20Hamas%20has%20threatened%20to%20hold%20off%20on%20releasing%20more%20hostages%20if%20Israel%20fails%20to%20meet%20its%20aid%20obligations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20of%20the%20three%20hostages%20brings%20the%20total%20number%20of%20hostages%20released%20since%20the%20ceasefire%20began%20to%2019.%20However%2C%20many%20more%20hostages%20remain%20in%20captivity%2C%20and%20efforts%20are%20ongoing%20to%20secure%20their%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20in%20Gaza%20remains%20dire%2C%20with%20thousands%20of%20people%20left%20homeless%20and%20without%20access%20to%20basic%20necessities%20like%20food%2C%20water%2C%20and%20electricity.%20The%20international%20community%20has%20called%20for%20an%20immediate%20end%20to%20the%20violence%20and%20for%20all%20parties%20to%20work%20towards%20a%20lasting%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20related%20development%2C%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20recent%20comments%20calling%20for%20Palestinians%20to%20be%20moved%20permanently%20out%20of%20Gaza%20have%20been%20widely%20condemned.%20The%20comments%20have%20been%20seen%20as%20inflammatory%20and%20have%20exacerbated%20tensions%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20situation%20continues%20to%20unfold%2C%20all%20eyes%20are%20on%20the%20release%20of%20the%20remaining%20hostages%20and%20the%20maintenance%20of%20the%20ceasefire.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftbody%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftable%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739611980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fb8dun3ig_israeli-hostages-afp_625x300_15_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-releases-3-israeli-hostages-for-369-palestinian-prisoners-7716463%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20hostages%2C%20who%20were%20seized%20by%20Hamas%20militants%20during%20an%20attack%20on%20October%207%2C%202023%2C%20were%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20International%20Committee%20of%20the%20Red%20Cross%2C%20whichthen%20transported%20them%20to%20Israeli%20forces.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-releases-3-israeli-hostages-for-369-palestinian-prisoners-7716463%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Team%20India%20players%2C%20including%20Rohit%20and%20Virat%2C%20head%20for%20CT%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%2