74527%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERanveer%20Allahbadia's%20controversial%20remarks%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20an%20episode.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ram%2C%20who%20was%20on%20the%20judges%20panel%20in%20one%20of%20the%20episodes%20of%20the%20now-deleted%20'%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Findias-got-latent-row-who-said-what-as-samay-raina-forced-to-remove-all-youtube-episodes-7708513%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia's%20Got%20Latent%3C%2Fa%3E'%2C%20released%20an%20official%20statement%20two%20days%20after%20he%20appeared%20before%20the%20Maharashtra%20Cyber%20Department%20amid%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20regret%20being%20part%20of%20IGL.%20I%20wish%20the%20show%20had%20not%20included%20some%20jokes%20that%20caused%20such%20hurt.%20The%20sensibilities%20of%20a%20paying%20audience%20in%20a%20show%20can%20differ%20from%20a%20larger%20YouTube%20audience%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20might%20have%20kept%20some%20jokes%20out%20of%20the%20episode%2C%20but%20I%20am%20nobody%20to%20tell%20Samay%20or%20the%20makers%20what%20jokes%20to%20keep%20and%20which%2C%20if%20any%2C%20words%20to%20beep.%20It%20is%20their%20call%2C%20and%20I'm%20sure%20they%20don't%20take%20that%20responsibility%20lightly%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ram%2C%20who%20was%20a%20former%20judge%20in%20the%20reality%20TV%20show%20Roadies%2C%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20news%20seems%20to%20have%20its%20own%20agenda%20regarding%20the%20ongoing%20IGL%20investigation.%20Statements%20I%20have%20made%20are%20being%20spun%20to%20make%20it%20sound%20different.%20Since%20their%20version%20is%20out%2C%20I'd%20like%20to%20put%20out%20mine%20as%20well%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F7CSvFeEWcC%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F7CSvFeEWcC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Raghu%20Ram%20(%40tweetfromRaghu)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FtweetfromRaghu%2Fstatus%2F1890665305740894700%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2015%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20freedom%20of%20speech%20is%20meaningless%20without%20the%20freedom%20to%20offend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOffence%20is%20often%20taken%20even%20when%20none%20is%20intended.%20But%20of%20course%2C%20I%20am%20sorry%20if%20I%20have%20actually%20caused%20hurt%20to%20anyone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20comedians%20%26quot%3Bpush%26quot%3B%20boundaries%2C%20call%20out%20society%20and%20speak%20truth%20to%20power%20while%20entertaining.%20%26quot%3BBut%20no%20comedian%20sets%20out%20to%20hurt%20sentiments.%20And%20they%20would%20be%20the%20first%20to%20apologise%20if%20they%20did.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20hope%20society%20maintains%20a%20proper%20perspective%20on%20the%20scale%20of%20this%20issue%20compared%20to%20others%20that%20need%20more%20outrage%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20actor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ram%20is%20among%20at%20least%2050%20people%20who%20have%20been%20summoned%20to%20record%20their%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20statement%20comes%20days%20after%20Mr%20Allahbadia%2C%20widely%20known%20by%20his%20online%20moniker%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Franveer-allahbadia-loses-nearly-50-000-followers-after-crass-remarks-7691739%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBeerBiceps%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%2C%20sparked%20massive%20controversy%20with%20his%20remarks%20about%20parents%20and%20sex%20during%20an%20episode%20of%20'India's%20Got%20Latent'%2C%20which%20also%20featured%20content%20creators%20like%20Ashish%20Chanchlani%2C%20Jaspreet%20Singh%20and%20Apoorva%20Mukhija%2C%20who%20goes%20by%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BThe%20Rebel%20Kid%26quot%3B%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWould%20you%20rather%20watch%20your%20p