-to-a-man-michelle-obama-elon-musks-father-errol-musks-bizarre-claim-7716293%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pariksha%20Pe%20Charcha%3A%20%26quot%3BBe%20Smarter%20Than%20Smart%20Phone%2C%26quot%3B%20Sadhguru%20Tells%20Students%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESpiritual%20leader%20and%20Isha%20Foundation%20chief%20Jaggi%20Vasudev%20or%20Sadhguru%20told%20students%20that%20they%20have%20to%20be%20smarter%20than%20their%20smart%20phones%2C%20while%20urging%20them%20to%20not%20treat%20exams%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bchallenge%20to%20their%20intelligence%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20students%20during%20Pariksha%20Pe%20Charcha%2C%20he%20said%20that%20exams%20are%20just%20a%20step%20to%20evaluate%20if%20students%20are%20fit%20to%20go%20to%20the%20next%20step%20of%20education.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20the%20grass%20or%20that%20motorcycle%2C%20you%20should%20think%20what%20is%20the%20physics%2C%20math%20and%20chemistry%20of%20it.%20Educations%20gives%20you%20fundamentals%20and%20eventually%20an%20access%20to%20life.%20To%20find%20this%20access%2C%20one%20aspect%20is%20active%20dynamic%20intelligence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20student's%20query%20on%20addiction%20to%20social%20media%20and%20the%20phone%2C%20he%20said%20that%20a%20person%20should%20decide%20how%20to%20use%20a%20smart%20phone%2C%20not%20the%20other%20way%20round.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20there%20is%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20overthinking%2C%20as%20one%20must%20think%20beyond%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do%20something%20worthwhile.%20%26quot%3BYou%20may%20call%20it%20stress%20or%20anxiety%2C%20but%20the%20problem%20is%20that%20you%20don't%20know%20how%20to%20keep%20your%20mind%20aligned.%20What%20is%20not%20well%20aligned%20will%20cause%20friction%2C%20further%20causing%20stress%2C%26quot%3B%20Sadhguru%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20the%20power%20of%20meditation%2C%20the%20spiritual%20leader%20said%2