%20basis%2C%20with%20similar%20flights%20bringing%20back%20Indian%20nationals%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks%20until%20all%20undocumented%20immigrants%20have%20returned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20US%20military%20plane%20carrying%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdeporting-104-indians-in-a-military-aircraft-cost-us-over-1-million-dollars-7654064%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E104%20deported%20Indians%3C%2Fa%3E%20landed%20on%20February%205.%20Of%20them%2C%2033%20each%20were%20from%20Haryana%20and%20Gujarat%2C%2030%20from%20Punjab%2C%20three%20each%20from%20Maharashtra%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20two%20from%20Chandigarh.%20Many%20of%20these%20migrants%20had%20spent%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20money%20on%20promises%20of%20legal%20entry%20into%20the%20US.%20Instead%2C%20they%20endured%20gruelling%2C%20multi-country%20treks%20arranged%20by%20human%20traffickers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Indians%20landed%2C%20many%20horror%20stories%20followed%20about%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20they%20were%20transported%20from%20the%20US%20to%20India.%20A%20video%20shared%20by%20the%20US%20Border%20Patrol%20also%20showed%20the%20migrants%20being%20handcuffed%20and%20their%20legs%20shackled.%20As%20they%20deboarded%20the%20plane%2C%20visuals%20showed%20the%20Indians%20made%20to%20a%20shuffled%20walk%20-%20something%20that%20is%20commonly%20associated%20with%20hardened%20criminals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20manner%20of%20these%20deportations%20triggered%20a%20furious%20response%20from%20the%20Opposition%20in%20India%2C%20who%20questioned%20why%20the%20Centre%20could%20not%20send%20a%20plane%20to%20bring%20back%20its%20citizens%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bhumane%20manner%26quot%3B.%20Amid%20this%20furore%2C%20they%20have%20yet%20again%20raised%20questions%20over%20how%20the%20second%20batch%20of%20Indians%20would%20be%20deported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20eyes%20will%20be%20on%20the%20US%20aircraft%20which%20will%20land%20today%20in%20Amritsar%20bringing%20back%20illegal%20immigrants.%20Will%20the%20deportees%20be%20handcuffed%20and%20their%20legs%20tied%20with%20ropes%3F%20It%20is%20a%20test%20for%20Indian%20diplomacy%2C%26quot%3B%20Congress%20leader%20P%20Chidambaram%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAll%20eyes%20will%20be%20on%20the%20U.S.%20aircraft%20which%20will%20land%20today%20in%20Amritsar%20bringing%20back%20illegal%20immigrants.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnWill%20the%20deportees%20be%20handcuffed%20and%20their%20legs%20tied%20with%20ropes%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt%20is%20a%20test%20for%20Indian%20diplomacy%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20P.%20Chidambaram%20(%40PChidambaram_IN)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPChidambaram_IN%2Fstatus%2F1890590066185064809%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2015%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECentre's%20response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20had%20responded%20to%20the%20Opposition's%20criticism%20saying%20that%20the%20deportations%20by%20the%20US%20were%20organised%20and%20executed%20by%20the%20Immigration%20and%20Customs%20Enforcement%20(ICE)%20-%20which%20provides%20the%20use%20of%20restraints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20we%20have%20been%20informed%20by%20ICE%20that%20women%20and%20children%20are%20not%20restrained.%20Further%2C%20the%20needs%20of%20deportees%20including%20during%20transit%2C%20related%20to%20food%20and%20other%20necessities%2C%20including%20possible%20medical%20emergencies%20are%20attended%20to.%20During%20toilet%20breaks%2C%20deportees%20are%20temporarily%20unrestrained%20if%20needed%20in%20that%20regard%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20also%20informed%20that%20such%20actions%20by%20the%20US%20authorities%20were%20%26quot%3Bnot%20new%26quot%3B%20and%20revealed%20the%20data%20of%20the%20deported%20Indians%20in%20the%20last%2015%20years.%20A%20total%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-many-indians-deported-from-us-in-last-15-years-s-jaishankar-shares-data-7653267%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E15%2C756%20illegal%20Indian%20immigrants%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20deported%20to%20India%20from%20the%20US%20since%202009%20-%20of%20which%202019%20saw%20the%20most%20number%20of%20deportations%20(2%2C042)%2C%20followed%20by%201%2C889%20in%202020%2C%20the%20year%20when%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20hit%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPunjab%20Chief%20Minister%20vs%20Centre%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20second%20batch%20of%20deported%20Indians%20is%20set%20to%20land%20in%20Amritsar%20today%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fillegal-indian-migrants-bhagwant-manns-defame-punjab-claim-over-deportation-flights-bjps-reply-7714795%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPunjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%3C%2Fa%3E%20criticised%20the%20Centre%2C%20accusing%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%20of%20deliberately%20trying%20to%20%26quot%3Bdefame%26quot%3B%20the%20state%20by%20choosing%20Amritsar%20as%20the%20landing%20site%20for%20the%20flights.%20According%20to%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leader%2C%20it%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bpart%20of%20conspiracy%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20BJP%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20second%20plane%20carrying%20Indian%20citizens%20who%20allegedly%20illegally%20migrated%20to%20the%20US%20will%20land%20in%20Amritsar%20tomorrow.%20The%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20should%20tell%20the%20criteria%20based%20on%20which%20Amritsar%20was%20selected%20to%20land%20the%20aircraft.%20You%20select%20Amritsar%20to%20defame%20Punjab.%20So%2C%20at%20the%20time%20when%20PM%20Modi%20and%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20were%20meeting%2C%20they%20(US%20authorities)%20must%20have%20been%20putting%