A%20trial%20opens%20the%20doors%20for%20a%20more%20non-invasive%20approach%20to%20understanding%20the%20specifics%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20heart%20health.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMore%20women-specific%20research%20will%20create%20a%20clearer%20picture%20of%20how%20heart%20disease%20affects%20women%2C%20how%20their%20bodies%20respond%20to%20treatment%2C%20and%20ultimately%2C%20how%20we%20can%20provide%20them%20with%20the%20best%20possible%20care.%20We%20need%20data-driven%20insights%2C%20not%20assumptions.%20This%20study%20is%20a%20crucial%20first%20step%20in%20that%20direction%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Rohit%20Singh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20key%20message%20is%20that%20women%20are%20unique%2C%20not%20just%20socially%2C%20but%20biologically%20as%20well.%20We%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20rely%20on%20assumptions%20based%20on%20male-centric%20research.%20In%20this%20era%20of%20advanced%20technology%2C%20we%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20remain%20in%20the%20dark%20about%20women%E2%80%99s%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20there%E2%80%99s%20one%20thing%20I%20want%20other%20women%20to%20know%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20this%3A%20don%E2%80%99t%20wait.%20If%20you%20experience%20any%20chest%20pain%2C%20discomfort%2C%20or%20breathlessness%2C%20seek%20help%20immediately%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Priya.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20take%20our%20health%20seriously%20because%20it%20can%20make%20all%20the%20difference.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EInformation%20appearing%20in%20this%20material%20is%20for%20general%20disease%20and%20therapy%20awareness%20only.%20Nothing%20contained%20in%20this%20material%20constitutes%20medical%20advice.%20Please%20consult%20your%20doctor%20for%20medical%20advice%20or%20any%20question%20or%20concern%20you%20may%20have%20regarding%20your%20health%20condition.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Leila%20Badyari%20Castelino%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20cla